snippet.title: Rainbow Six Siege: High Calibre Story Trailer | Ubisoft [NA]
snippet.description: A new operator is joining Rainbow Six Siege. On November 30, learn how Thorn's devastating gadget impacts the battlefield in the new Season, High Calibre.
